	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_FIRSTGREETING_1">
			<Text>Hello, my name is Loolilalu. My people and I are lost in this strange place and simply wish to return home. Please show us mercy.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_DEFEATED_1">
			<Text>Very well. Please, at least spare my people, I don't care what you do with me.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_GREETING_POLITE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>(giggles) I like you already! Please, call me Loo.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_GREETING_NEUTRAL_HELLO_1">
			<Text>Hello, good knight!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_GREETING_HOSTILE_HELLO_1">
			<Text>I'm not one to talk foul of others, however I'll tell you that you're getting awfully close to being barred from entering my kingdom's walls ever again.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_HOSTILE_AGGRESSIVE_MILITARY_WARNING_1">
			<Text>I can see your forces outside my walls. I'm confident that we'll hold out despite your unwarranted aggression.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_HOSTILE_HUMAN_SMALL_ARMY">
			<Text>My advisors tell me your military situation is looking a little dicey. Don't worry, I get it! We all get distracted. Let's hope the other nations here don't find out.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_EXPANSION_SERIOUS_WARNING_1">
			<Text>You break my heart. Why settle so close to us? Did we do something to upset you?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_REQUEST">
			<Text>Ah, you must be the kind samaritan sent to us by God... to help us with our recent catastrophe.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_LUXURY_TRADE">
			<Text>Why let resources go to waste? Come, let us trade!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_ATTACKED_BETRAYED">
			<Text>Okay, wait. Y-You did what now?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_ATTACKED_EXCITED">
			<Text>My people are ready to fight! Don't think we'll take your aggression lying down!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_ATTACKED_HOSTILE">
			<Text>You're unbelievable. Come then, let's settle this for good.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_LEADER_TADC4_LOOLILALU_DECLAREWAR_1">
			<Text>My profuse apologies to you, I must attack now. I'm simply doing what must be done to help my people. Just keep your citizens out of the way, I don't want to harm them...</Text>
		</Row>
